0179 - Fruits and Tree Nuts, Not Elsewhere Classified Summary > BUSSELTON FARMS PTY LTD is an Australian proprietary company. Its operations cover fruits and tree nuts, not elsewhere classified. The company is not involved in the import or export of goods. BUSSELTON FARMS PTY LTD is headquartered in Southbank, Victoria. It is headed by director Thierry Bedard. For the 2025 financial year, the company reported revenue of $21.58 million. Its net profit totalled $3.26 million. BUSSELTON FARMS PTY LTD forms part of the agriculture, forestry, and fishing industry sector.
